                "url": "/topics/making"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630270",
        "quote": "Every kid goes to school full of questions about meaning. You know, 'What's my place in the universe? What does it mean to be a human being? What are human beings?' Existing courses cannot help you answer those questions. They can't even help you ask them.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David Christian",
            "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630270"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
