                "url": "/topics/about"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630274",
        "quote": "When very large stars die, they create temperatures so high that protons begin to fuse in all sorts of exotic combinations, to form all the elements of the periodic table. If, like me, you're wearing a gold ring, it was forged in a supernova explosion.",
