    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_825129",
        "quote": "Big History's not going to replace existing educational courses. It's not an attack on specialisation. It is simply the argument that specialisation needs to be complemented with an overview, which I think is scientific commonsense.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David Christian",
            "url": "/quotes/david_christian_825129"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Big",
                "url": "/topics/big"
            },
            {
                "name": "Needs",
                "url": "/topics/needs"
            },
            {
                "name": "Which",
                "url": "/topics/which"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630269",
        "quote": "I had this feeling that, somehow, we ought to be teaching not just the history of particular nations or particular regions, but the history of humanity.",
