                "url": "/topics/the_history_of"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630271",
        "quote": "Our goal is to see Big History become a normal part of high school curricula. I'd love to see it being taught in lots of languages. A global course.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David Christian",
            "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630271"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Normal",
                "url": "/topics/normal"
            },
            {
                "name": "Big",
                "url": "/topics/big"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630276",
        "quote": "I believe human beings mark a threshold in the development of the planet, of course, but it is only part of the picture. What Big History can do is show us the nature of our complexity and fragility and the dangers that face us, but it can also show us our power, with collective learning.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David Christian",
            "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630276"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Complexity",
                "url": "/topics/complexity"
            },
            {
                "name": "Big",
                "url": "/topics/big"
            },
            {
                "name": "Dangers",
                "url": "/topics/dangers"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630278",
        "quote": "In literature classes, you don't learn about genes; in physics classes you don't learn about human evolution. So you get a fragmented view of the world. That makes it hard to find meaning in education.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David Christian",
            "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630278"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Education",
                "url": "/topics/education"
            },
            {
                "name": "Learn",
                "url": "/topics/learn"
            },
            {
                "name": "Genes",
                "url": "/topics/genes"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630279",
        "quote": "Modern scientific knowledge appeared piecemeal. Historians wrote about human history; physicists tackled the material world; and biologists studied the world of living organisms. But there were few links between these disciplines, as researchers focused on getting the details right.",
        "author": {
            "name": "David Christian",
            "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630279"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            },
            {
                "name": "Scientific",
                "url": "/topics/scientific"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
