                "name": "Means",
                "url": "/topics/means"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/david_christian_630286",
        "quote": "Unfortunately, historians have become so absorbed in detailed research that they have tended to neglect the job of building larger-scale maps of the past.",
